%N A395669 Expansion of g^7*(4-3*g)/(7-6*g)^2, where g = 1+x*g^7 is the g.f. of A002296.
%F A395669 Sum_{k>=1} a(k-1) * x^k/k = (1/14) * log( Sum_{k>=0} binomial(7*k+7,k) * x^k ).
%F A395669 a(n) = A395667(n)/(n+1) = (1/14) * (binomial(7*n+6,n) + Sum_{k=0..n+1} 6^(n+1-k) * binomial(7*n+7,k)).
%o A395669 (PARI) a(n) = (binomial(7*n+6, n)+sum(k=0, n+1, 6^(n+1-k)*binomial(7*n+7, k)))/14;
